+    { "criterion": "AC5: Accessibility compliance maintained (WCAG 2.1 AA)", "status": "fail", "evidence": "Select in CodeBlockFontSection.tsx is not given an id, so its label has no verified programmatic association (WCAG 2.1 SC 1.3.1/4.1.2). No keyboard-navigation or focus-visibility test coverage was added despite Task 11 requiring it." },
